config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    primaryColor: "#FDF6EC"
    primaryTextColor: "#45210E"
    primaryBorderColor: "#45210E"
    lineColor: "#45210E"
    actorBkg: "#F4BA17"
    actorTextColor: "#45210E"
    actorBorder: "#45210E"
    noteBkgColor: "#FFF7E0"
    noteBorderColor: "#F4BA17"
    fontFamily: "Be Vietnam Pro, Arial, sans-serif"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as Buyer
    participant CH as Channel<br/>(API / OSS drop)
    participant OR as Orchestrator<br/>(qwen3-max)
    participant PA as Parser<br/>(qwen-vl-ocr / qwen-plus)
    participant CM as CatalogMatcher<br/>(embed v4 + qwen3-max)
    participant PE as PricingEngine<br/>(deterministic)
    participant DR as Drafter<br/>(qwen3-max)
    participant CR as Critic<br/>(recompute + qwen3-max)
    participant TS as Tablestore<br/>(memory + state)
    participant M as Manager (HITL)
    participant DP as Dispatch<br/>(PDF · OSS · mail)

    B->>CH: RFQ (VI/EN text · PDF · scan · xlsx)
    CH->>OR: run_quote(quote_id)
    OR->>TS: create session · status=parsing
    OR->>PA: extract line items
    PA->>PA: rasterize pages · vision/text extract
    PA-->>OR: RFQExtraction (confidence, spans)
    OR->>CM: match lines
    CM->>TS: vector_search + full_text_search (catalog)
    TS-->>CM: candidates
    CM-->>OR: MatchResults (needs_confirmation flags)
    OR->>PE: price_quote(matches, customer)
    Note over PE: tier price · VAT 8%/10%<br/>margin · Decimal only — no LLM math
    PE-->>OR: PricedQuote
    OR->>TS: retrieve episodic memory (importance × decay)
    TS-->>OR: top-3 memories (≤1200 tokens)
    OR->>DR: draft bilingual quote (+memories, +SOP)
    DR-->>OR: Quote (numbers checksum-verified)
    OR->>CR: validate
    CR->>PE: recompute all totals
    PE-->>CR: exact match ✓
    CR-->>OR: CriticReport (flags)
    OR->>TS: status=pending_approval · persist state
    Note over OR,M: ⏸ DURABLE PAUSE — function exits.<br/>Approval may arrive hours later. A new<br/>invocation resumes from Tablestore state.
    M->>OR: approve (or revise ↩ Drafter, max 3)
    OR->>TS: status=approved · audit(actor=human)
    OR->>DP: dispatch
    DP->>DP: WeasyPrint bilingual PDF (Be Vietnam Pro)
    DP->>TS: episodic memory write (importance init)
    DP-->>M: presigned URL · email sent
    DP-->>B: Báo giá / Quotation QM-2026-NNNN
